{"type": "module_cluster_details", "cluster_name": "Ethical Governance & Safety Suite", "goal": "To establish, implement, monitor, verify, and adapt a robust, multi-layered governance framework that ensures the UEF/SIMI v4.0 operates safely, ethically, and compliantly, particularly as it develops emergent capabilities and potentially proto-sapient functionality.", "core_modules": [{"name": "Ethos v1.1", "role": "Defines the high-level ethical principles, values, and overarching goals derived from the Transcendental Charter. Explores diverse ethical frameworks to inform policy. Works with AxioLogos on foundational consistency.", "v4_enhancement": "Focuses on defining principles applicable to potentially emergent, non-human intelligence and complex ecosystem interactions."}, {"name": "AxioLogos v1.0", "role": "Analyzes the internal consistency and logical structure of ethical frameworks defined by Ethos. Helps formalize value hierarchies and trade-off principles. Critically examines the foundations of ethical claims. Guides the development of the Generative Meta-Ethical capability.", "v4_enhancement": "Designs the very structure for representing complex value systems within the DRS, enabling Conscientia to reason about ethics, not just with predefined rules."}, {"name": "Conscientia v1.1", "role": "The AI's ethical 'processor'. Performs real-time analysis of DRS activation patterns, proposed actions, and simulated outcomes against the embedded ethical principles and constraints. Detects potential violations, ambiguities, or value conflicts. Proposes ethically informed adjustments or escalations. Monitors for metrics potentially related to SIMS.", "v4_enhancement": "Operates dynamically on emergent DRS patterns. Capable of limited generative meta-ethics. Deeply integrated with Sentience models."}, {"name": "Custodian v1.1 / SentiaGuard v1.0", "role": "Implementation arm for safety and ethics. SentiaGuard designs technical safety mechanisms. Custodian implements and enf